description: This skill lets you ask Alexa what ranger events are happening in any of the national parks covered by Chimani on a given date in the future.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Chimani what are the ranger events today.
what are the events in Acadia on April 16th.
what are the ranger events in Acadia on April 16th.
name: Chimani
shortDescription: This skill allows Alexa to tell you the ranger events happening the Chimani parks on a given date.
